data.title: Deep Creek Lake, Maryland
data.text:
Wednesday, 8/14/2024, 6:00pm

The “brothers from another mother” are sure to keep you entertained throughout the entire show, playing music that is influenced and inspired by bands like The Beatles, The Eagles and The Rolling Stones.

Friday, 8/16/2024, 4:00pm

Combining their love for mountain music with classic rock, outlaw country and just at touch of folk, they've created their own style of playing. Come check them out!

Friday, 8/16/2024, 9:00pm

Garrett Mabe is a Guitarist/Singer/Songwriter who began playing bars at the age of 13 and at 25 year old already has 12 years of musical experience under his belt. He delivers the passion, vocal ability, and guitar work you are looking for in a dynamic performer. He and his band of some of the best Baltimore musicians will put on not only a great sounding show, but a performance to match!

Saturday, 8/17/2024, 1:30pm

Not even a “Reign Dance” can keep this band away! Playing dance music from the 60’s and todays top hits, Occasional Reign always keeps you groovin’ on the dance floor. Grab your umbrellas and your dancing shoes; this band is as unpredictable as the weather!

Saturday, 8/17/2024, 9:00pm

Have a blast with this upbeat and fun band! Let's Go! will have you dancing all night!

Sunday, 8/18/2024, 2:00pm

Garrett Mabe is a Guitarist/Singer/Songwriter who began playing bars at the age of 13 and at 25 year old already has 12 years of musical experience under his belt. He delivers the passion, vocal ability, and guitar work you are looking for in a dynamic performer. He and his band of some of the best Baltimore musicians will put on not only a great sounding show, but a performance to match!

Tuesday, 8/20/2024, 6:00pm

The Gashouse Annie band has opened for many top artists over the last 40+ years. This includes appearances with legends Willie Nelson, Barbara Mandrell & Glen Campbell, Loretta Lynn and newer country artists Aaron Tippin, Toby Keith, Kenny Chesney and Brooks & Dunn. This band plays a mix of classic Rock, Country, Blues, Acoustic, and Gospel!

Friday, 8/23/2024, 4:00pm

Surrender Dorothy, from Cumberland, MD will have you out of your seat and onto the dance floor with their genius style of cover songs from both classic rock and top 40s. Toto will be begging for more and so will you.

Friday, 8/23/2024, 9:00pm

A wild three-piece powerhouse with influences from all genres of music. Boathouse is one of the most original, exciting, high-energy bands that create a unique experience every time! Dock your boat and rock with Boathouse!

Saturday, 8/24/2024, 1:30pm

Funkadelic at its finest! Everybody’s movin’, eveybody’s groovin’ along to the rock/funk machine with a 3-piece horn section! Truly an experience like none other, don’t forget to bring your boogie shoes!

Saturday, 8/31/2024, 9:00pm

Covering 250 hit songs, Undercover plays everything from the 60’s to today and sound just like the hits they cover. You don’t want to hide “under cover” and miss this professional party band!

Sunday, 9/1/2024, 1:30pm

A six piece band that plays all the oldies and goodies. The best dance music from a simpler time.

Monday, 9/2/2024, 1:00pm

It’s all in the name! The premier dance band out of Cumberland, MD is sure to keep you on the dance floor and feeling “Hot, Hot, Hot”! Keeping the sound of Motown authentic and performing all your favorite songs from the electrifying era!

Saturday, 9/7/2024, 1:30pm

Known in the Baltimore/Washington area for over 30 years as the hottest dance band with killer horns and vocals, The Shades feature music from the classic Motown hits of the 60's through the hot horn sound of 70's and 80's R&B and Rock and Roll.

Thursday, 9/12/2024, 8:00pm

The Honi House Band consists of a rotating collection of local artists and musicians. The band brings a new sound every time they get together and play; you never know who might show up!

Saturday, 9/14/2024, 1:30pm

Just what the doctor ordered! Shake your groove thang to this upbeat, energetic, and soulful rhythm and blues—with a little bit of good ol’ rock and roll—band!

Saturday, 9/21/2024, 9:00pm

Have a blast with this upbeat and fun band! Let's Go! will have you dancing all night!

Friday, 9/27/2024, 9:00pm

A wild three-piece powerhouse with influences from all genres of music. Boathouse is one of the most original, exciting, high-energy bands that create a unique experience every time! Dock your boat and rock with Boathouse!

Saturday, 9/28/2024, 1:30pm

What do you get when you combine backgrounds of music education, extensive touring experience and national radio promotion? Nashville Recording Artist, The Kenton Sitch Band. Current, edgy original sound and hottest country radio favorites!
